Greg and Joren Harris
raised their children to love Jehovah.

00:26:26.635 --> 00:26:30.005 line:90% position:50% align:center
What decisions did they make along the way?

00:26:31.740 --> 00:26:33.775 line:10% position:50% align:center
When a person makes a sacrifice,

00:26:33.775 --> 00:26:35.310 line:10% position:50% align:center
they give up something

00:26:35.310 --> 00:26:37.012 line:10% position:50% align:center
for something that they consider

00:26:37.012 --> 00:26:38.413 line:10% position:50% align:center
is of higher value.

